						Embrace clarity and control over your financial journey, today and every day. Let's make financial management not just easy, but also empowering.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		@* Financial Clarity *@
		<div class="mt-4 bg-white rounded-lg lg:flex justify-center items-center">
			<div class="lg:order-last w-100 p-4">
				<img class="w-100 rounded-lg" src="/Images/Financial_Clarity.png" />
			</div>
			<div class="lg:order-first w-100 text-center">
				<p class="font-bold text-2xl xl:text-4xl 2xl:text-6xl text-blue-600 lg:[text-shadow:_0_1px_0_rgb(255_0_0_/_100%)] hover:lg:[text-shadow:_0_5px_0_rgb(0_0_255_/_100%)] hover:text-red-600 duration-500"> Financial Clarity</p>
