					Gain unparalleled insight into your financial health with our 'Financial Clarity' feature. Effortlessly track your income, expenses, and savings,
					all presented in an intuitive and easy-to-understand format. Make informed decisions and achieve your financial goals with clarity and confidence.
					For more information about website click <a class="text-green-500 hover:text-black" href="/Services"> here</a>
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		@* Simplified Savings *@
		<div class="mt-4 bg-white rounded-lg lg:flex justify-center items-center">
			<div class="lg:order-first w-100 p-4">
				<img class="w-100 rounded-lg" src="/Images/Simplified_Savings.png" />
			</div>
			<div class="lg:order-last w-100 text-center">
				<p class="font-bold text-2xl xl:text-4xl 2xl:text-6xl text-blue-600 lg:[text-shadow:_0_1px_0_rgb(255_0_0_/_100%)] hover:lg:[text-shadow:_0_5px_0_rgb(0_0_255_/_100%)] hover:text-red-600 duration-500"> Simplified Savings</p>
